    {
        "content": "<p>A typo. It should be a. It’s copy pasta trying to reduce the actual code to a simple example. Anyhow, fixing the type of slot made the compiler happy I think. At least now it is complaining about something else 😅 Thanks!</p>",
        "id": 388069079,
        "sender_full_name": "Andreas Hindborg",
        "timestamp": 1693388498
