    {
        "content": "<p>does this work?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">fn</span> <span class=\"nf\">init_b</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">val</span>: <span class=\"nc\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">init</span>::<span class=\"n\">pin_init_from_closure</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"n\">slot</span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">__pinnned_init</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">slot</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">cast</span>::<span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">())</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">})</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 388076432,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1693391313
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I assume you mean like this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span> <span class=\"nf\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span>: <span class=\"kt\">u64</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">init_b</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">})</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>It does not work:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Text only\"><pre><span></span><code>error[E0277]: the trait bound `impl init::PinInit&lt;B&lt;u64&gt;, _&gt;: init::PinInit&lt;B&lt;T&gt;, _&gt;` is not satisfied\n   --&gt; /home/aeh/src/linux-rust/linux/rust/kernel/revocable.rs:124:9\n    |\n124 | /         pin_init!( Self {\n125 | |             b &lt;- init_b(a),\n    | |             - required by a bound introduced by this call\n126 | |         })\n    | |__________^ the trait `init::PinInit&lt;B&lt;T&gt;, _&gt;` is not implemented for `impl init::PinInit&lt;B&lt;u64&gt;, _&gt;`\n    |\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><code>slot.cast::&lt;T&gt;()</code> also does not work, but <code>as *mut T</code> does.</p>",
        "id": 388078473,
        "sender_full_name": "Andreas Hindborg",
        "timestamp": 1693392100
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Sorry, forgot initializer for <code>A</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span> <span class=\"nf\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span>: <span class=\"kt\">u64</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">init_b</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">A</span>::<span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">)),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">})</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Then compiler says: </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Text only\"><pre><span></span><code>error[E0277]: the trait bound `impl init::PinInit&lt;B&lt;A&gt;&gt;: init::PinInit&lt;B&lt;T&gt;, _&gt;` is not satisfied\n   --&gt; /home/aeh/src/linux-rust/linux/rust/kernel/revocable.rs:125:9\n    |\n125 | /         pin_init!( Self {\n126 | |             b &lt;- init_b(A::new(a)),\n    | |             - required by a bound introduced by this call\n127 | |         })\n    | |__________^ the trait `init::PinInit&lt;B&lt;T&gt;, _&gt;` is not implemented for `impl init::PinInit&lt;B&lt;A&gt;&gt;`\n    |\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 388080707,
        "sender_full_name": "Andreas Hindborg",
        "timestamp": 1693393000
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You are trying to initialize a <code>C&lt;T&gt;</code>, but actually it should be a <code>C&lt;A&gt;</code>.</p>",
